description.p:
1.


A sensor cooperating with a vibration transmissive outer panel of a motor vehicle, such sensor being capable of responding to a discrete tapping action of the operator;


2.


A means of conveying the sensor output to an electronic circuit module of the invention for the purpose of processing sensor output;


3.


The circuit module being capable of processing sensor output to provide a means for actuating the motor vehicle electric door lock system.
